lt_of_forall_lt_of_lt:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →₀ » -/
theorem lt_of_forall_lt_of_lt (a b : lex («expr →₀ » α N)) (i : α) :
    (∀ j < i, of_lex a j = of_lex b j) → of_lex a i < of_lex b i → a < b := fun h1 h2 => ⟨i, h1, h2⟩
#align lt_of_forall_lt_of_lt lt_of_forall_lt_of_lt

theorem lex_lt_of_lt_of_preorder [preorder N] (r) [is_strict_order α r] {x y : «expr →₀ » α N} (hlt : x < y) :
    ∃ i, (∀ j, r j i → x j ≤ y j ∧ y j ≤ x j) ∧ x i < y i :=
  dfinsupp.lex_lt_of_lt_of_preorder r (id hlt : x.to_dfinsupp < y.to_dfinsupp)
#align lex_lt_of_lt_of_preorder lex_lt_of_lt_of_preorder

lex_def:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →₀ » -/
theorem lex_def {r : α → α → Prop} {s : N → N → Prop} {a b : «expr →₀ » α N} :
    finsupp.lex r s a b ↔ ∃ j, (∀ d, r d j → a d = b d) ∧ s (a j) (b j) :=
  iff.rfl
#align lex_def lex_def
